        <anchor n="T.50.2061.0757a24"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011013">潤州竹林寺</placeName><persName key="A010097">曇璀</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0757a25"/><persName key="A010097">釋曇璀</persName>，俗姓顧氏，<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳郡</placeName>人也。肇國著姓，其來<lb
ed="T" n="0757a26"/>彌光。丞相<note resp="sgsz">指<persName key="A019015">顧琮</persName>。詳《新唐書．卷七十四下》。</note>有佐命之勳，尚書<note resp="sgsz">指<persName key="A019017">顧少連</persName>。詳《新唐書．卷一百六十二》。</note>有挺濟之譽。衣<lb
ed="T" n="0757a27"/>冠鼎胄，<placeName key="PL000000021580">太嶽</placeName>峻<placeName key="PL000000021580">岱峯</placeName>之高；令問徽猷，<placeName key="PL000000000150">江</placeName><placeName key="PL000000026396">漢</placeName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0757a28"/><placeName key="PL000000000197">南國</placeName>之紀。星象降精，靈祇効祉，德備胎教，<lb
ed="T" n="0757a29"/>香符夢徵。玄珪應上聖之祥，神寶蓄<placeName key="PL000000000193">河</placeName><placeName key="PL000000005527">汾</placeName><pb ed="T" n="0757b" xml:id="T50.2061.0757b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0757b01"/>之氣。特受異準，生而不凡，襁褓之日而童<lb
ed="T" n="0757b02"/>蒙來求，佩觽之時而忘身殉道。和敏而純<lb
ed="T" n="0757b03"/>素，溫恭而克明，神器夙昭，清風漸扇。遂勉節<lb
ed="T" n="0757b04"/>出塵，栖心物表，金經祕藏，一日萬言，不逾<lb
ed="T" n="0757b05"/>歲敘，而大經淹通。遂於晚年緬懷宗匠，始<lb
ed="T" n="0757b06"/>事<placeName key="PL000000008579">牛頭山</placeName><persName key="A003867">融大師</persName>。<persName key="A003867">融</persName>醇懿瓌雄，<placeName key="PL000000000083">東夏</placeName>之<persName key="A001361">達磨</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0757b07"/>歟！梵幢寶柱，大海津梁，目以上根，乃誨<ref type="person" target="#A010097">之</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0757b08"/>曰：「色聲為無生之鴆毒，受想是至人之坑阱。<lb
ed="T" n="0757b09"/>致遠多泥，<ref type="person" target="#A010097">子</ref>不務乎？」<persName key="A010097">璀</persName>默而審之，直轡獨<lb
ed="T" n="0757b10"/>上，飡甘露味，飲蒲<anchor xml:id="beg0757002"/>萄<anchor xml:id="end0757002"/>漿，猶金翅不食異<lb
ed="T" n="0757b11"/>類，<persName key="A002869">帝釋</persName>無共鬼居。迺晦迹<placeName key="PL000000008734">鍾山</placeName>，斷其漏習，<lb
ed="T" n="0757b12"/>養金剛定，趣大能位，納衣空林，多歷年所。<lb
ed="T" n="0757b13"/>時<placeName key="PL000000010798">淮南</placeName>導首<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName><persName key="A010098">覺禪師</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000000197">江左</placeName>名德<placeName key="PL000000008820">建業</placeName><persName key="A010099">如<lb
        ed="T" n="0757b14"/>法師</persName>，咸<anchor xml:id="beg0757sgsz2"/>杖<anchor xml:id="end0757sgsz2"/>錫方來，降心義體，握珠懷寶，虛<lb
ed="T" n="0757b15"/>往實歸。<persName key="A002099">則天皇母</persName>臨朝，龔行佛事，高其道<lb
ed="T" n="0757b16"/>業，周勤詔書。時<placeName key="PL000000009026">棲霞</placeName><persName key="A010101">約法師</persName>，梵門之秀傑，躬<lb
ed="T" n="0757b17"/>以敦勸朝天，抗詔皇明，恐未然也。<persName key="A010097">璀</persName>曰：「<persName key="A019020"><anchor xml:id="beg0757003"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0757003"/><lb
        ed="T" n="0757b18"/>伯</persName>辭<persName key="A002434">帝舜</persName>之師，<persName key="A002707"><anchor xml:id="beg0757sgsz3"/>干<anchor xml:id="end0757sgsz3"/>木</persName>謝<persName key="A002864">文侯</persName>之命，<persName key="A009180">玄暢</persName>以<lb
ed="T" n="0757b19"/>善論而抗<ref type="person" target="#A002604">宋主</ref>，<persName key="A001204">惠遠</persName>不下山而傲<placeName key="PL000000037386">齊后</placeName>，彼<lb
        ed="T" n="0757b20"/>何人哉！」由是遁北阜，踰東岡，考槃雲冥，<lb
ed="T" n="0757b21"/>後止于<placeName key="PL000000011013">竹林</placeName>之隩，葺宇簋缶而告老焉。既<lb
ed="T" n="0757b22"/>而紹列聖之鴻徽，繼前賢之能事，翼亮皇<lb
ed="T" n="0757b23"/>梵，保寧天人。俄端然入定，七日而滅，春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0757b24"/>六十二。是歲<date key="j19738691973869" when-iso="0692-03-02">天授三年二月六日</date>也。<ref type="date" target="#j19738701973870">翌日</ref>，依<lb
ed="T" n="0757b25"/>天竺法火化，遺骸收灰建塔，士庶含酸，悉<lb
ed="T" n="0757b26"/>皆號慟。門弟子<persName key="A010103">僧感</persName>、<persName key="A010104">僧頵</persName>等刻石紀事，奉<lb
        ed="T" n="0757b27"/>全師<anchor xml:id="beg0757sgsz4"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0757sgsz4"/>。正議大夫使持節<placeName key="PL000000010986">潤州</placeName>刺史<placeName key="PL000000026322">汝南郡</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0757b28"/><persName key="A006600">昇</persName><note resp="sgsz">潤州刺史查無名中有「昇」者。惟南唐<persName key="A006600">李昪</persName>（<placeName key="PL000000010411">海州</placeName>人）曾任潤州刺史。</note>嚮風遐想，悅而久之，褒德尚賢，贊成厥<lb
ed="T" n="0757b29"/>美焉。</p>
